tasks.description:
**Goal:** Cut feature/v0.2.0 off develop and bump workspace version to 0.2.0.

**Files:** Modify Cargo.toml (workspace.package.version + internal-dep version pins).

**Verify:** `cargo build --workspace && cargo metadata --no-deps --format-version 1 | python3 -c "import json,sys;d=json.load(sys.stdin);print(set(p['version'] for p in d['packages']))"` → {'0.2.0'}

```json:metadata
{"files": ["Cargo.toml"], "verifyCommand": "cargo build --workspace", "acceptanceCriteria": ["on feature/v0.2.0 branch", "workspace.package.version = 0.2.0", "all internal deps pinned to 0.2.0", "build clean"]}
```
